Bxd4 Rac8 $11 {[%cal Ye7f6,Ye7c5] and Black is doing well.}) 10... h6 11. e3 {
Zatonskih,A (2430)-Nguyen,E (2143) USA-ch (Women) 59th 2019 (8) 1/2} ({The
prophylactic} 11. Ng2 $5 {was more precise.}) (11. Rc1 Bxb3 $1 {this knight
