White didn't get the point.} (12. Qb5+ {was still necessary.}) 12... Rb8 $1 13.
Qa6 Bb4+ 14. Bd2 Bxd2+ 15. Nxd2 O-O 16. Nxg6 hxg6 17. Nb3 Qe7 $17 {[%cal Ge5c4]
;Andersen,M (2601)-Berkes,F (2647) DEN-chT 1920 58th 2019 (6.1) 0-1 Not only
