[%csl Yd4][%cal Ge8c7,Gc7e6,Ge7f6,Gc6d4,Ge6d4];Nakamura,H (2787)-Caruana,F 
(2801) Sinquefield Cup 2nd 2014 (5) 0-1 starting a nice regroupment to create
