Bxc6 Qxc6 17. Qxc6+ bxc6 18. e5 Ne8 19. Nf1 c5 20. Be3 Nc7 $17 {[%cal Yc7e6];
Pajeken,J (2323)-Gustafsson,J (2645) Bundesliga 1920 2019 (5.8) 0-1 with clear
