c5 $1 {Black gives the pawn back but gets a good position anyway.} 19. dxc5
Nxc5 20. Rxd8+ Bxd8 $1 21. Nxc5 Qxc5 22. axb5 a5 $1 $15 {[%csl Ga5][%cal Yd8b6]
and Black is at least fine.}) (8. Rb1 $5 {Another creative invention by Dubov.
